1.First u run the autocad application it will ask some information fill all the
blanks and close the window.
2.reopen the autocad appliction u will see an window with some request code.
3.now open the keygen (Keygen should be "run as administrator" ).
4.now click on "mem patch"(u will see a small window written as "sucessfully patched")
5.now copy the request code at the starting window and paste in the keygen and 
  click on generate, now u will see a ACTIVATION CODE.
6.Now copy the ACTIVATION CODE and paste into the autocad mechanical lincence window.
